title: Anthem Vegan
description: Vegan food vendor setting up stands at SD area farmers markets - check webpage for updates. Sundays in Hillcrest Farmers Market 9am-2pm, Tuesdays in PB Farmers Market 2-7pm, Wednesdays in OB Farmers Market 4pm-8pm, Thursdays in SPCA 11am-3pm, Friday-Saturday in North Park 11am-2:30pm.
